":606970,"uid":48796,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T02:12:18.000Z","msg":"香港體育界食屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 圍威喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 磨滅運動員青春<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T03:49:54.000Z","msg":"一班肥過閪，淨係識呃飲呃食嘅撚樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bada3da4bbe11dd448b024b94ebbc9e3e8a79a17","tid":606970,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T03:51:05.000Z","msg":"不如叫所有運動員唔再玩運動把啦"},{"pid":"9fb0fcbb493c800e55cd4dde627cfc11801aa185","tid":606970,"uid":43314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T06:31:46.000Z","msg":"香港全部體育總會都係自己人圍威喂，埋唔到去嘅唔駛指意有得代表香港"},{"pid":"fa039eef59df177a8797524d7f9bb33325fe999f","tid":606970,"uid":24044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T06:34:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://programme.rthk.hk/assets/images/rthk/tv/headliner/originals/mfile_857_109626_3_l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fprogramme.rthk.hk%2Fassets%2Fimages%2Frthk%2Ftv%2Fheadliner%2Foriginals%2Fmfile_857_109626_3_l.jpg&h=af939a67&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}